  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Nothing beats a good Swiss breakfast. The daily buffet breakfast offers a range of hot and cold items, including many local products from Interlaken and the surrounding area.</p>
<p>In the evenings enjoy a three-course Half Board menu with choice of main dish. </p>
<p>Both meals will be held at the L'Ambiance restaurant within the hotel. </p>
<p>When weather permits, both breakfast and dinner can be enjoyed on the terrace, which overlooks the beautiful Aare River.</p>
<p>In afternoons and evenings you can enjoy wine, cocktails and beer in the cosy Le Vieux Rivage bar and terrace (payable locally). </p>]]></cateringDescription>
