  <description><![CDATA[<p>Preserving tradition, the Grand Hotel Beau Rivage brings a historical ambience to Interlaken. From its grand exterior, the extravagant and elegant style continues inside. The hotel is beautifully furnished throughout, and offers all the modern comforts you need. Located on the River Aare, and just a few minutes from the town centre and Interlaken Ost train station, you'll be perfectly situated for any mountain excursions or lake activities.</p>
<h2>Al fresco terrace dining</h2>
<p>Enjoy the peaceful gardens and al fresco dining with magnificent views of the Jungfrau, Eiger and Mönch mountains. Share your culinary delights with great company and excellent service, overlooking the turquoise waters of the River Aare. Serving sustainable ingredients that have been locally sourced, the L'Ambiance restaurant is a pleasure for everyone. </p>
<h2>Relax and unwind </h2>
<p>The wellness area with indoor pool, sauna, steam bath and fitness centre, is the ideal place to refresh and leave behind the stresses of everyday life. With classic massages and facial treatments (payable locally), you can unwind and indulge until your hearts content. And, after a busy day exploring the Bernese Oberland, you'll always have a comfortable bed to fall back on at the end.</p>]]></description>
