  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> are around 23m² and sleep two to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). These rooms have a south-facing balcony (above the hotel entrance and driveway, facing towards the mountains).</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<p>On arrival/departure a taxi/porter service is provided to transfer you to/from the station.</p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF3.50 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 15 years and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Steps into property:<strong> 0</strong></li>
<li>Adapted rooms:<strong> 1</strong></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
